title: Blood on the Land (1960) Full Length Western

sources.title: Blood on the Land (1960) Full Length Western
sources.description:
Jeb Drummond (Everett Sloane) is a greedy sheepherder determined to fatten his animals on the Ponderosa grasslands: he takes Adam hostage to force Ben to sign over part of the Ponderosa.
 
#22
Director: Felix E. Feist 
Writer: Robert E. Thompson
Stars: Pernell Roberts, Dan Blocker, Michael Landon
Genres: Bonanza, Classics, Cult, TV, Western
